'''MaKhalathi''' ke batho ba [[Aferika Borwa]]. Ka [[Seisimane]] ba bitswa "Coloureds" goba "People of Colour". Ka [[Seburu]] (''Afrikaans'') ba bitswa "Kleurlinge" goba "Bruinmense".

MaKhalathi ba sala gagolo mo porofense ya [[Kapa Bophirima]] le [[Kapa Bokone]].

